## Agent Response Structure Used:
```typescript
interface AgentResponse {
  status: 'success' | 'error'
  result: {
    message: string
    sessions?: Session[]
    calendar_events?: CalendarEvent[]
    conflicts?: Conflict[]
    notes?: Note[]
    venue_directions?: VenueDirections
    action_prompt?: string
  }
  metadata: {
    agent_name: string
    timestamp: string
    language: string
  }
}
```

